                    <div class="panel-body">
                        <ul>
                            <li>
                                Register for an account with us, and designate yourself
                                as a "Pet Owner".
                                <br /><br />
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                You'll then get to fill out profile details for yourself
                                and your pet(s).
                                Don't have time right now?  Come back and fill in your
                                details later when you can have some fun with it.
                                <br /><br />
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                Your pet(s)' profile(s) will be visible from within your
                                profile.
                                Be sure to put in everything that your Pet Care Provider
                                would need or want to know when caring for your pet!
                                <br /><br />
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                You can come back and edit or update your or your pet(s)'
                                details any time you like, or add new photos of your
                                pets!
                                <br /><br />
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                Once you have your profile details filled out, you'll be
                                taken to your profile page.  On the right-hand side,
                                you'll see a listing of all Pet Care Providers in your
                                area who are experienced caring for your type of pet!
                                On their card you'll see their profile photo, name, and
                                "badges" for what kind of pet(s) they're experienced
                                with.  Click on their card, and you can check out their
                                full profile.
                                <br /><br />
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                Once you find one you are interested in, send them a
                                private message from inside Petopia, to protect your
                                private information.  Once you decide this is the one
                                for you and your pet, you can make arrangements with
                                them for the services you and your pet need.
                                <br /><br />
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                You can see a Pet Care Provider's schedule information
                                from their profile, to see if they are available when
                                you need them.  Their rate information is also posted
                                here.  Payments are also handled from inside Petopia
                                for you!
                                <br /><br />
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                You can rate your Pet Care Provider each time they
                                provide service for your pet, and see their cumulative
                                ratings from all past care transactions.
                                <br /><br />
                                Please remember to rate your provider -- these ratings
                                help other Pet Owners like you know they can trust this
                                provider with their beloved pet!
                                <br /><br />
                                Did your Pet Care Provider do something to "go the
                                extra mile?"  For instance, did they find your pet had
                                left an unexpected mess in your home, and clean it up
                                for you instead of just leaving it?
                                <br /><br />
                                You can also let other Pet Owners know if a provider
                                is on-time or not, (or if they forgot to arrive!),
                                if they check-in as arranged, if they gave good
                                feed-back on their viist.
                                <br /><br /><br />
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                Your Pet Care Provider can also check in with you
                                during and after providing care for your pet!  Would you
                                like to know for sure that your pet's provider arrived?
                                That your sweet pet got their meds, or dinner, or let
                                out/in, or exercised on time?   Taken to and returned
                                from their appointment?  With Petopia, your provider can
                                check in with this information and it will be sent via
                                the route you choose in real-time.
                                <br /><br />
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                The check-in notes your Pet Care Provider leaves, will
                                become part of your pet's record -- so if you need to
                                have a different provider for subsequent care visits,
                                the new provider will have access to helpful notes about
                                your pet.
                                <br /><br />
