                                </span>
                            </p>
                            <p style="padding-left: 13px; margin-bottom: 0;">
                                Love pets and want a rewarding side-hustle? <br />
                                Here's how it works for you:
                            </p>
                        </div><!-- end 'panel-title'\'our_panel_title' div -->
                    </div><!-- end 'panel-heading'\'our_panel_heading' div -->
