                        <ul>
                            <li>
                                Register for an account with us, and designate yourself
                                as a "Pet Care Provider".
                                <br /><br />
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                You'll then get to fill out profile details for yourself.
                                Don't have time right now?  Come back and fill in your
                                details later when you can have some fun with it.
                                <br /><br />
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                You can come back and edit or update your details any
                                time you like, add new photos, "badges" for types of
                                pets you take care of, or descriptions of your experience
                                &amp; qualifications.
                                <br /><br />
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                Once you have your profile details filled out, you'll be
                                taken to your profile page to review it.  But, before you
                                can "go live" and accept care assignments, you'll have
                                to complete a background report.  This will be reflected
                                on your profile so Pet Owners know you're trust-worthy
                                to care for their special pets in their home!
                                <br /><br />
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                Once everything has cleared, you'll be good to go.
                                Just indicate on your scheduler the days and times you
                                are available, so Pet Owners can see it.
                                <br /><br />
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                When a Pet Owner contacts you via private message from
                                within Petopia, the two of you can get to know each other
                                a little bit and settle any outstanding details, and you
                                can get the instructions you'll need in order to
                                complete your pet care assignment.
                                <br /><br />
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                Once each assignment is complete, the Pet Owner will be
                                sent an invoice, and payments will go directly to you!
                                <br /><br />
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                Just as Pet Owners can rate you and your service, you
                                can also rate the Pet Owner.  Did they not pay in a
                                timely fashion?  Were there hazards left that impeded
                                your ability to care for their pet?  Things not as
                                they'd been explained to you?
                                <br /><br />
                                Conversely (and hopefully!) was your Pet Owner and the
                                Pet you cared for a lot of fun and just as described?
                                Did the Pet Owner do something nice to make your job a
                                little easier?  Leave you a special treat?
                                <br /><br />
                                Either way, let other Pet Care Providers know what
                                they're in for!
                                <br /><br /><br />
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                You can use check-ins as arranged with the Pet Owner,
                                and add another level of customer service to boost your
                                ratings (and possibly get an extra treat next time!)
                                <br /><br />
                                Let your Pet Owner know that their pet got their meds,
                                food, exercise, made it to and from their appointment or
                                play-date okay, and if they did anything during this time
                                their owner may like or need to know about.
                                <br /><br />
                                You can check in with the Pet Owner during and/or after
                                your care visit -- however you arranged it with your Pet
                                Owner, or when/if there is something you feel they should
                                know right away.  They will get your check-in details
                                via their device in real-time!
                                <br /><br /><br />
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                Your check-in information will stay on that Pet's
                                record -- this way you can leave helpful notes for the
                                next Pet Care Provider, if it's not you!
                                <br /><br />
                            </li>
                            <li>
